<title>USA: Hemagen says to buy back up to 300,000 shrs.</title>
<headline>Hemagen says to buy back up to 300,000 shrs.</headline>
<dateline>WALTHAM, Mass. 1997-05-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hemagen Diagnostics Inc said Wednesday its board authorized the company to buyback up to 300,000 common shares.</p>
<p>The company said the purchases are subject to management's discretion and applicable securities laws.</p>
<p>The company said it has cash resources that can be beneficially invested in its own common stock at current market prices.</p>
<p>It said the authorization expires on April 30, 1998 and may be made in any amount up to the aggregate maximum in open market or private purchases.</p>
